title: BelowDeckMed: 911 Collie
description:
Below Deck Med takes a sad turn in this super sized episode when Anastasia quits her chef spot and Collie considers throwing himself on the knife for the girl who loves cake. Enjoy!
To hear this week's premium bonus breaking down the Married to Medicine season 7 trailer and watch video versions of our recaps, become a member over at Patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens.
